'''Chris Gardner''' is an author of the ''[[Star Wars: Build the Millennium Falcon (De Agostini)|Star Wars: Build the Millennium Falcon]]'' part works.
He also worked on ''[[The Official Star Wars Fact File]]'', published [[2002]] through [[2005]]. He has also contributed to the UK Star Wars Magazine and ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' interviewing such [[Star Wars]] luminaries as the late [[Michael Sheard]] ([[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Kendal Ozzel/Legends|Kendal Ozzel]]), [[Gil Taylor]] (cinematographer), [[Robert Watts]] (producer), [[Albert Clarke]] (stills photographer) and [[Ian Liston]] ([[Snowspeeder/Legends|snowspeeder]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]]/[[All Terrain Armored Transport/Legends|AT-AT]] Driver).

